UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT; CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION; HONIG, BILL; 
NATIONAL ASSOCIATION FOR THE ADVANCEMENT OF COLORED PEOPLE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
