</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Unrestricted free agent Spencer Tillman, left unprotected by the Houston 
Oilers, signed a two-year contract worth $475,000 with the San Francisco 49ers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
